headline: Interactive Brokers (IBKR): Valuation Check After New Access to Brazil’s B3 and UAE Markets
summary: Interactive Brokers Group (IBKR) is quietly widening its global footprint again, now giving clients direct access to Brazilian stocks on B3 alongside UAE equities on ADX and DFM. This marks a strategic nudge toward deeper emerging market exposure. See our latest analysis for Interactive Brokers Group. headline: Private Markets: Musk’s SpaceX targets 2026 IPO at valuation of $1.5T
summary: Elon Musk’s SpaceX is moving ahead with plans for an initial public offering that would seek to raise “significantly more” than $30B at a market value of about $1.5T. Meanwhile, Agentic engineering startup Port raised $100M in a Series C funding round at $800M valuation.
